<eesti>V&auml;lisministeeriumi diplomaatilise koosseisu ametiastmed </eesti>
<inglise>Official ranks of diplomatic staff of Ministry of Foreign Affairs </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;lisministeeriumi diplomaatilise koosseisu ametiastmed on: </eesti>
<inglise>The official ranks of the diplomatic staff of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs are: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kantsler - secr&eacute;taire g&eacute;n&eacute;ral, permanent under secretary; </eesti>
<inglise>1) kantsler - secr&eacute;taire g&eacute;n&eacute;ral, permanent under secretary; </inglise>
<eesti>2) osakonna peadirektor - directeur g&eacute;n&eacute;ral de d&eacute;partement, director general of department; </eesti>
<inglise>2) osakonna peadirektor - directeur g&eacute;n&eacute;ral de d&eacute;partement, director general of department; </inglise>
<eesti>3) b&uuml;roo direktor - directeur de bureau, director of division; </eesti>
<inglise>3) b&uuml;roo direktor - directeur de bureau, director of division; </inglise>
<eesti>4) n&otilde;unik - conseiller, counsellor; </eesti>
<inglise>4) n&otilde;unik - conseiller, counsellor; </inglise>
<eesti>5) ministeeriumi esimene (I) sekret&auml;r - premier secr&eacute;taire de minist&egrave;re, first secretary of ministry; </eesti>
<inglise>5) ministeeriumi esimene (I) sekret&auml;r - premier secr&eacute;taire de minist&egrave;re, first secretary of ministry; </inglise>
<eesti>6) ministeeriumi teine (II) sekret&auml;r - deuxi&egrave;me secr&eacute;taire de minist&egrave;re, second secretary of ministry; </eesti>
<inglise>6) ministeeriumi teine (II) sekret&auml;r - deuxi&egrave;me secr&eacute;taire de minist&egrave;re, second secretary of ministry; </inglise>
<eesti>7) ministeeriumi kolmas (III) sekret&auml;r - troisi&egrave;me secr&eacute;taire de minist&egrave;re, third secretary of ministry; </eesti>
<inglise>7) ministeeriumi kolmas (III) sekret&auml;r - troisi&egrave;me secr&eacute;taire de minist&egrave;re, third secretary of ministry; </inglise>
<eesti>8) ministeeriumi ata&scaron;ee - attach&eacute; de minist&egrave;re, attach&eacute; of ministry. </eesti>
<inglise>8) ministeeriumi ata&scaron;ee - attach&eacute; de minist&egrave;re, attach&eacute; of ministry. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
